menunggu puluhan tahun.

526
00:34:35,739 --> 00:34:37,258
Itu bagus, 'kan?

527
00:34:37,259 --> 00:34:38,578
Dukunglah V-Day!

528
00:34:38,579 --> 00:34:40,418
Katakan, "Tidak. Kali ini tidak."

529
00:34:40,419 --> 00:34:44,419
Kali ini, kita hidup bersama.

530
00:34:47,739 --> 00:34:50,658
Kalian serius? Ini?

